  "type": "TEXT",
  "title": "Understanding Posture",
  "lessonText": "Proper posture is essential for playing guitar comfortably and effectively.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Sit up straight with your back supported.\n- Keep your shoulders relaxed and down.\n- Position the guitar on your right leg (for right-handed players).\n- Hold the neck of the guitar with your left hand, keeping your wrist straight.\n- Use your right hand for strumming or picking, maintaining a relaxed arm position."
  }
}
